    date: "2019-12-22",
    author: "Ingeman",
    excerpt: "Ocean recovery targets are moving targets: recovery potential shifts in time as environmental conditions change, varies across space due to connectivity and heterogeneity, and differs among stakeholders with different values. Successful recoveries require redefining recovery to embrace multiple goals, research that anticipates future recovery dynamics, and policies nimble enough to keep pace with change.",
