    date: "2019-03-15",
    author: "Pretorius",
    excerpt: "High activity level was negatively associated with purple sea urchin survival when facing California spiny lobster predators, but this effect was strong for smaller urchins and weaker for large urchins. Covering behavior alone did not predict survival, though smaller urchins with greater covering behavior survived better.",
